try():
```
try(() -> read(item.embeddedJson, 'application/json')) match {
  case { success: true  } -> $.result
  case { success: false } -> { parseError: $.error.message }
}
```
Null-safe + default:
```
payload.?customer.?address.?city default 'UNKNOWN'
// chained optional selectors — no NPE
```
Conditional key inclusion:
```
{
  id: payload.id,
  (discount: payload.discount) if payload.?discount != null,
  status: payload.status default 'PENDING'
}
```
Array-safe transform pattern:
```
payload map (item, index) ->
  try(() -> {
    amount: item.amount as Number,
    date: item.date as Date {format: 'dd-MM-yyyy'}
  }) match {
    case { success: true  } -> $.result
    case { success: false } -> { _error: true, _index: index, _reason: $.error.message, raw: item }
  }
```
